import React, { Component } from 'react';

class PayForms extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <form>
        <fieldset>
          <legend>Informações do Comprador</legend>
          <label htmlFor="fullname">
            Nome completo:
            <input type="text" name="fullname" data-testid="checkout-fullname" />
          </label>
          <label htmlFor="email">
            Email:
            <input type="email" name="email" data-testid="checkout-email" />
          </label>
          <label htmlFor="CEP">
            CEP:
            <input type="number" name="CEP" data-testid="checkout-cep" />
          </label>
          <label htmlFor="phone">
            Telefone:
            <input type="number" name="phone" data-testid="checkout-phone" />
          </label>
          <label htmlFor="address">
            Endereço:
            <input type="text" name="address" data-testid="checkout-address" />
          </label>
          <input type="submit" value="Finalizar compra" />
        </fieldset>
      </form>
    );
  }
}

export default PayForms;
